[Event]
ChartRendered
[EventDescription]
Fired after the chart has been rendered.
[Event]
SeriesClicked
[EventDescription]
Fired when the user clicks on a data point in the chart.
[Parameter1]
seriesName
[Parameter1Type]
STRING
[Parameter1Description]
Name of the series clicked
[Parameter2]
category
[Parameter2Type]
STRING
[Parameter2Description]
Category label of the clicked point
[Parameter3]
value
[Parameter3Type]
REAL
[Parameter3Description]
Data value of the clicked point
